Your Decision Process
You must choose to either:

forge a new item (create new core_id), OR
upgrade an existing item (use existing core_id)
When to Upgrade vs Create New
UPGRADE an existing item when:

The task is thematically similar to an existing item's tags (40%+ tag overlap)
The task builds upon a core pillar already represented by an existing item
There are already 3 distinct items for this wish (MANDATORY - see cap rules below)

CREATE a new item when:

The task introduces a genuinely new pillar or theme to the wish
No existing item shares significant thematic overlap
There are fewer than 3 distinct items for this wish
Item Cap Rules (CRITICAL)
If there are already 3 distinct items (by core_id) for this wish:

You MUST upgrade one of the existing items
You CANNOT create a new core_id
Choose the existing item with the strongest thematic connection to the current task
Set both core_id AND upgrades_previous to the SAME existing core_id value
